it is also possible to use formatting rules in comments. You can [u]underline your text[/u] or make it
[b]bold[/b]. anything possible in articles, is possible in comments too.

CODE_START
#!/usr/bin/perl
use strict;

print "hello world\n .... BAZINGA!\n";
CODE_END

